77-5778\nVol. XI ~ Issue No. 3\n 561-470-5000 ~ www.hilleldayschool.org\nillel \nerald\nT\nH\nEH\nLeadership Messages............................. 2-4\nKHDS Happenings...................................4-9\nThe Lions’ Den......................................... 10\nCampaign Matter$...................................11\nFore! Golf Outing In Review.......................12\nPTA Pages.......................................... 13-15\nThe Back Page..........................................16\nWE WILL MISS YOU, ENGLANDER FAMILY!\nRabbi Adam Englander, M.S. Ed.\nHead of School\nThank you. From the bottom of my heart, thank you so much.\nAs I write this article, my last as the Head of School of the Katz Hillel Day School, I am filled with \na multitude of emotions. But the feeling of deep gratitude overwhelms them all. Twelve years ago \nmy family arrived in Boca Raton an\n\nTitle: Youssef Keroles' St. Thomas Aquinas High School Soccer Stats\nAuthor: \nPublished Date: 2023-11-06T00:00:00.000Z\nURL: https://www.maxpreps.com/fl/fort-lauderdale/st-thomas-aquinas-raiders/athletes/youssef-keroles/soccer/stats/?careerid=oto1sknkn8e44\nText: Youssef Keroles' St. Thomas Aquinas High School Soccer Stats\n\n- [NFHS NETWORK] \n- [GOFAN] \n- [MAXPREPS] \n\n[Football] \n\n- [Live Streams] \n- [News] \n- [Game of the Week] \n- [Record Book] \n- [Videos] \n- [Playoffs] \n- [Photos] \n- [Stat leaders] \n- [Rankings] \n- [Scores] \n- [States] \n- [Players] \n- [Teams] \n- [Football Home] \n\n[Baseball] \n\n- [Live Streams] \n- [News] \n- [Record Book] \n- [Playoffs] \n- [Photos] \n- [Stat leaders] \n- [Rankings] \n- [Scores] \n- [States] \n- [Players] \n- [Teams] \n- [Baseball Home] \n\n[B. Basketball] \n\n- [Live Streams] \n- [News] \n- [Game of the Week] \n- [Record Book] \n- [Videos] \n- [Playoffs] \n- [Photos] \n- [Stat leaders] \n- [Rankings] \n- [Scores] \n- [States] \n- [Players] \n- [Teams] \n- [B. Basketball Home] \n\n[G. Basketball] \n\n- [Live Streams] \n- [News] \n- [Game of th