ng, ...\n\nNano letters 19 (12), 8673-8682, 2019\n\n[Broadband achromatic metasurface-refractive optics] \n\nWT Chen, AY Zhu, J Sisler, YW Huang, KMA Yousef, E Lee, CW Qiu, ...\n\nNano letters 18 (12), 7801-7808, 2018\n\n[Compact aberration‐corrected spectrometers in the visible using dispersion‐tailored metasurfaces] \n\nAY Zhu, WT Chen, J Sisler, KMA Yousef, E Lee, YW Huang, CW Qiu, ...\n\nAdvanced Optical Materials 7 (14), 1801144, 2019\n\n[Melanin-gamma rays assistants for bismuth oxide nanoparticles synthesis at room temperature for enhancing antimicrobial, and photocatalytic activity] \n\nAI El-Bata\n\nTitle: Kerolos Yousef\nAuthor: \nPublished Date: 2024-12-01T00:00:00.000Z\nURL: https://www.mrs.org/meetings-events/annual-meetings/archive/profile/Kerolos-Yousef-\nText: Kerolos Yousef\nSearch\nCloseSearch\n[![MRS_logo]] \nWelcome\n[My Account] \n[Logout] \n[Login] \n# Kerolos Yousef\n### Presentation History\n2024 MRS Fall Meeting &amp; Exhibit\n[Active Metasurface Based on TiO2/BTO Heterostructure] \nDec 1, 2024, 4:30 PM\n![] \nPress &amp; Public Relations Contact\n**Ryan Rebholz**\nCommunications Manager\nMaterials Research Society\n[Contact Us**] \n[Privacy Policy] |[Terms of Use] \n506 Keystone Drive, Warrendale, PA 15086-7537\nPhone: 724.779.3003 | Fax: 724.779.8313 |**Email:[[email&#160;protected]] **\n©Materials Research Society. All Rights Reserved.\nWeb Design &amp; Development by[**Matrix Group International, Inc.**] \n* [**] \n* [**] \n* [**] \n* [**] \n* [**] \n* [**] \n* [**]\n\nTitle: Kerolos M. A. Yousef | Capasso Group\nAuthor: \nURL: https://capasso.seas.harvard.edu/people/kerolos-m-yousef\nText: Kerolos M. A. Yousef | Capasso Group\n\n# Kerolos M. A. Yousef\n\nGraduate Student\n\n[kyousef@seas] \n\n[LinkedIn] \n\n[Google Scholar] \n\n## People\n\n- [Graduate Student]\n\nTitle: Keroles Riad\nAuthor: Become an author\nPublished Date: 2024-05-30T00:00:00.000Z\nURL: https://theconversation.com/profiles/keroles-riad-386853\nText: Keroles Riad – The Conversation\n[\n] \n[\n] \n[\n![The Conversation] \n] \nAcademic rigour, journalistic flair\n![] \n# Keroles Riad\n(He/Him)\n[\n## 4\nArticles\n] \n[\n## 0\nComments\n] \n*\nPostdoctoral Fellow, Nanotechnology,\n[Carleton University] \nDr. Keroles B. Riad is a Banting postdoctoral fellow at Carleton University. He is also a valedictorian and former Public Scholar at Concordia University where he received a Ph.D. degree from the individualized program developing new materials for 3D printing. He is the CEO of O Nanotech Solutions, a startup that provides flame-made metal oxide quantum dots at scale for a few hundred dollars a gram- an order of magnitude cheaper than the market. He is also the CEO of enuf, a spin-off B-corp of the “Waste Not, Want Not” student initiative he started at Concordia University for which he received the Quebec Lieutenant-Governor Youth Medal. Since the beginning of “Waste Not, Want Not” in 2016, the Concordia community doubled their annual composting, and each Concordian reduced their annual overall waste by 16%.\n## Experience\n*\n2022&ndash;present\nPostdoc\n\nTitle: Kiyash Monsef\nAuthor: \nPublished Date: 2025-01-01T00:00:00.000Z\nURL: https://www.goodreads.com/author/show/5821267.Kiyash_Monsef\nText: Kiyash Monsef (Author of Once There Was) ,\n\nDiscover new books on Goodreads\n\nSee if your friends have read any of Kiyash Monsef's books\n\n[Sign in with Facebook] \n\n[Sign in options] \n\n[Join Goodreads] \n\n## Kiyash Monsef’s Followers (66)\n\n# Kiyash Monsef\n\n[edit data] \n\n## Combine EditionsKiyash Monsef’s books\n\nAverage rating: 3.92\n\n· 3,039 ratings · 553 reviews · [12 distinct works] • [Similar authors] \n\n[Once There Was (Once There Was #1)] \n\n3.90 avg rating — 2,738 ratings — published 2023 — [34 editions] \n\nWant to Read saving…\n\n- Read\n- Currently Reading\n- Want to Read\n\nError rating book. Refresh and try again.\n\nRate this book\n\nClear rating\n\n1 of 5 stars2 of 5 stars3 of 5 stars4 of 5 stars5 of 5 stars\n\n[Bird of a Thousand Stories (Once There Was #2)] \n\n4.08 avg rating — 259 ratings — published 2025 — [14 editions] \n\nWant to Read saving…\n\nError rating book. Refresh and try again.\n\nRate this book\n\nClear rating\n\n1 of 5 stars2 of 5 stars3 of 5 stars4 of 5 stars5 of 5 stars\n\n[The Unbeatable Deck of Ronan Shin] by\n\n[Kiyash Monsef],\n\n[Helen Shewolfe Tseng] (Illustrator)\n\n4.42 avg rating — 24 rati\n\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772239944386}}
