{"type":"message","id":"59ee5344","parentId":"6e3e9966","timestamp":"2026-02-28T01:24:41.413Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call-96841514-bc20-4ffa-af2f-de9e1c852acd","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Title: OpenClaw + Polymarket: The Complete Prediction Market Trading Guide\nAuthor: OpenClaw Team\nPublished Date: 2026-02-17T00:00:00.000Z\nURL: https://openclawai.me/blog/polymarket-trading-guide\nText: OpenClaw + Polymarket: The Complete Prediction Market Trading Guide\n\nProduct\n\n[FeaturesCore capabilities & AI skills] [Smart TradingAutomated crypto trading] [Integrations13+ messaging platforms] [DownloadInstall & get started] \n\nLearn\n\n[BlogGuides, tutorials & news] [LearnStep-by-step learning path] [ResourcesDocs, API refs & tools] [Use CasesReal-world applications] \n\nCommunity\n\n[ShowcaseUser projects & builds] [TestimonialsWhat users are saying] \n\n[Get Started] \n\n[← Back to Blog] \n\nTrading2026-02-17\n\n# OpenClaw + Polymarket: The Complete Prediction Market Trading Guide\n\nPolymarket hit $12 billion in trading volume in January 2026 alone. AI agents are rapidly becoming the dominant participants in prediction markets, reacting to news and data faster than any human can. OpenClaw gives you a complete toolkit to deploy your own Polymarket trading agent—without writing a single line of code.\n\nThis guide covers everything: installing the Polymarket skill, understanding how the AI evaluates markets, configuring proven strategies, and ke\n\nTitle: Polymarket Review (2026): Global Guide, Fees, Risk, and How to Start | polymarket.help\nAuthor: polymarket.help\nPublished Date: 2026-02-22T00:00:00.000Z\nURL: https://polymarket.help/\nText: Polymarket Review (2026): Global Guide, Fees, Risk, and How to Start | polymarket.help\n\nWhat Polymarket Is\n\n## What is Polymarket, in plain English?\n\nPolymarket is a prediction market platform. Users buy and sell positions tied to outcomes of real-world events, and the market price is commonly read as an implied probability. For example, if a market price is around a certain level, many users interpret that level as the crowd's estimate of the likelihood of the outcome.\n\nThat framing matters because it changes how you should think about the product. Polymarket is not best approached as a casual “pick a side and hope” interface. It is more useful when you treat it as a probability market with rules, resolution criteria, execution costs, and risk management.\n\nIn official public-facing pages, Polymarket presents itself as a major prediction market platform and provides both a help center and documentation resources. Those public resources are useful because they let users verify basic questions (sign-up, fees, limit orders, trading limits, \n\nTitle: Polymarket Strategies 2026: 5 Proven Ways to Beat the Market\nAuthor: VPN07\nPublished Date: 2026-02-24T00:00:00.000Z\nURL: https://vpn07.com/en/blog/2026-polymarket-trading-strategies-win-prediction-markets-tips.html\nText: Polymarket Strategies 2026: 5 Proven Ways to Beat the Market\n\n# Polymarket Trading Strategies 2026: 5 Proven Ways to Beat the Market\n\nFebruary 24, 2026 16 min read Strategy\n\nImportant Context: Polymarket has matured significantly. With $1.5+ billion in weekly volume, the market is more efficient than ever. Strategies that worked in 2023 are largely obsolete. This guide focuses on what actually generates edge in 2026's competitive prediction market environment — based on analysis of top trader behaviors and verified returns.\n\nHere's a sobering statistic: 80% of Polymarket participants lose money over time. The platform is not a casino where luck evens out — it's an information market where the most informed, disciplined traders consistently extract value from less prepared participants. If you're in that 80%, the good news is the gap between losing and winning is about process, not luck.\n\nThe top 1% of Polymarket traders don't have crystal balls. They have systems. They approach each market with a structur\n\nTitle: How to Build polymarket Agent Skill | SkillMD.ai\nAuthor: SkillMD.ai\nPublished Date: 2026-02-01T00:00:00.000Z\nURL: https://skillmd.ai/how-to-build/polymarket-3/\nText: How to Build polymarket Agent Skill | SkillMD.ai\n\n## Quick Start\n\n1\n\n### Download\n\nGet the skill files as a ZIP package\n\n2\n\n### Import\n\nAdd SKILL.md to your AI assistant\n\n3\n\n### Use\n\nStart using the skill with Claude or Cursor\n\n[Download polymarket Skill] \n\n## Prerequisites\n\n- Basic understanding of how AI agent skills work\n- Git installed for version control\n- An AI coding assistant that supports SKILL.md files (Claude Code, Cursor, Codex, etc.)\n\n## File Structure\n\n```\npolymarket/\n├── references/api.md\n├── references/getting_started.md\n├── references/guides.md\n├── references/index.md\n├── references/learn.md\n├── references/llms.md\n├── references/other.md\n├── references/README.md\n├── references/realtime-client.md\n├── references/trading.md\n\n```\n\nThis skill contains 10 file(s). The main entry point is SKILL.md.\n\n## What is polymarket?\n\npolymarket is an agent skill designed to help you comprehensive polymarket skill covering prediction markets, api, trading, market data, and real-time websocket data streaming. build applications with polymarket services, monitor \n\nTitle: Polymarket Guide (2026): How to Trade Crypto Prediction Markets\nAuthor: \nPublished Date: 2026-02-22T00:00:00.000Z\nURL: https://masterpredictionmarkets.com/blog/polymarket-guide-how-to-trade-crypto-prediction-markets\nText: Polymarket Guide (2026): How to Trade Crypto Prediction Markets\n\n[Polymarket] processed more trading volume than every other prediction market combined during the 2024 US election cycle. That is not an exaggeration — individual markets on the platform saw hundreds of millions of dollars in total volume, and it cemented Polymarket as the dominant crypto-native prediction market in the world. If you are interested in trading event contracts and you want access to the deepest liquidity available, Polymarket is a platform you need to understand.\n\nThis guide covers everything you need to go from zero to placing your first trade: how the platform works, how to get funds on it, how to navigate markets, and — most importantly — how to think about finding edge. We trade prediction markets every day across multiple platforms, and we will share practical insights that go beyond what the official docs tell you.\n\n## What Is Polymarket?\n\nPolymarket is a prediction market exchange where you buy and sell shares in the o\n\nTitle: Polymarket’s New Rules Released: How to Build a New Trading Bot | Bee Network\nAuthor: \nURL: https://www.bee.com/66307.html\nText: Polymarket&#8217;s New Rules Released: How to Build a New Trading Bot | Bee Network\n![bee.com] \n[\n![bee.com] \n] \n[\n![] \nLogin\n![] \n] \n* [**Trending News\n] \n* [**Meme Launchpad\n] \n* [**AI Agents\n] \n* [**DeSci\n] \n* [**TopChainExplorer\n] \n* [**For Newbee\n] \n* [**100x Coins\n] \n* [**Bee Game\n] \n* [**Essential Websites\n] \n* [**Must-Have APP\n] \n* [**Crypto Celebrities\n] \n* [**DePIN\n] \n* [**Rookies Essential\n] \n* [**Trap Detector\n] \n* [**Basic Tools\n] \n**\n* [Advanced Websites] \n* [Exchanges] \n* [NFT Tools] \nHi,\nSign out\n![icon_install_ios_web] \n![icon_install_ios_web] \n![icon_install_android_web] \n[![bee.com]] \n[\nWeb3 Universe ] \n[\nGames ] \n[\nDApp ] \n[\nBee Hive ] \n[\nGrowing Platform ] \n[\nAD\n] \n[\n![bee.com] \nSearch\n] \n[\n![change language] \nEnglish\n![down app] \n] \n[![bee.com]] \n[![bee.com]] \n[![bee.com]] \n[\n![change language] \nRecharge Coins\n] \n[\nLogin\n] \n[\n![https://static.bee.com/wp-images/icon/icon_bee_muen_moble.png] \n] \n[\n![back] \n] \n[\n![https://static.bee.com/wp-images/icon/icon_bee_sreach_pc.png] \n] \n[\n![https://static.bee.com/wp-images/icon/icon_bee_com_logo.png] \n] \n![https://static.bee.com/wp-im\n\nTitle: Polymarket Skills - Power Your AI Agent for Prediction Markets\nAuthor: Polymarket Skills\nURL: https://polyskills.xyz/\nText: Polymarket Skills - Power Your AI Agent for Prediction Markets\n[ ![Polymarket Skills] \nPolymarket Skills\n] \nOpen Source Skills Directory\n#\nPolymarket Skills\nPower your AI agents with real-time prediction market data. Search markets, execute trades, and analyze portfolios instantly.\n[\nBrowse Skills\n] [\nGitHub\n] \nagent.ts\n# Market Discovery\n\\> Check odds for \"Will GPT-5 launch in 2025?\"\nGPT-5 Release 2025 Vol: $4.2M\nYES\n32¢\nNO\n68¢\n\\> Buy 1000 YES shares at market\\_\n## Available Skills\n3\n[\nv1.0.0\n### Polymarket Market Intelligence\nDiscover and analyze Polymarket prediction markets. Real-time odds, volume, trending markets, and breaking news.\nMarkets Odds News\n1240\n85\n![] Polymarket\n] [\nv1.0.0\n### User Trading Insights\nAccess user trading history, portfolio analytics, P&amp;L analysis, and leaderboard rankings.\nAnalytics Portfolio History\n1240\n85\n![] Polymarket\n] [\nv1.0.0\n### Polymarket Trading\nExecute trades, manage orders, and interact with the Polymarket CLOB. Place buy/sell orders, manage positions, and automate trading strategies.\nTrading Orders CLOB\n856\n42\n![] Polymarket\n]\n\nTitle: What is Polymarket\nURL: https://help.polymarket.com/en/articles/13364060-what-is-polymarket\nText: What is Polymarket | Polymarket Help Center\n[Skip to main content] \n[![Polymarket Help Center]] \nSearch for articles...\nTable of contents\n[] \n[] \n[] \n[] \n[All Collections] \n[Getting Started] \nWhat is Polymarket\n# What is Polymarket\nPolymarket is the world’s largest prediction market, allowing you to stay informed and profit from your knowledge by betting on future events across various topics.\nUpdated over a month ago\nTable of contents\n[] \n[] \n[] \n[] \nStudies show prediction markets are often more accurate than pundits because they combine news, polls, and expert opinions into a single value that represents the market’s view of an event’s odds. Our markets reflect *accurate, unbiased, and real-time probabilities* for the events that matter most to you. Markets seek truth.\n## **​Quick Overview**\n*\nOn Polymarket, you can representing future event outcomes (i.e. “Will TikTok be banned in the U.S. this year?”)buy and sell shares\n*\nShares in event outcomes are between 0.00 and 1.00 , and every pair of event outcomes (i.e. each pair of “YES” + “NO” shares) is fully collateralized by $1.00 USDC.always pricedUSDC\n*\nShares are created\n\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772241881403}}
{"type":"message","id":"7abe3c4e","parentId":"59ee5344","timestamp":"2026-02-28T01:25:01.776Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Polymarket هو منصة أسواق التنبؤ حيث يمكنك شراء وبيع مواقف مرتبطة بنتائج أحداث واقعية. إليك ما يمكنك فعله:\n\n## المهارات والقدرات:\n\n**تحليل الأسواق:**\n- البحث عن الأسواق الحالية واحتمالاتها\n- تحليل حجم التداول والاتجاهات\n- متابعة الأخبار العاجلة التي تؤثر على الأسواق\n- تحليل المحافظ ونتائج التداول\n\n**التداول:**\n- تنفيذ صفقات شراء/بيع\n- إدارة الطلبات والأوامر\n- أتمتة استراتيجيات التداول\n- مراقبة المراكز المفتوحة\n\n**الذكاء الاصطناعي:**\n- تقييم الأسواق باستخدام الذكاء الاصطناعي\n- التفاعل مع الأخبار والبيانات بشكل أسرع من البشر\n- تحليل الأنماط والاتجاهات\n- اتخاذ قرارات تداول بناءً على البيانات\n\n**الأدوات المتقدمة:**\n- بيانات السوق في الوقت الفعلي\n- تحليل الاحتمالات\n- متابعة الأسواق الشائعة\n- تحليل أداء المتداولين الآخرين\n\nالمنصة تعالج أكثر من مليار دولار في الحجم الأسبوعي، والذكاء الاصطناعي أصبح المشارك السائد في أسواق التنبؤ."}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"arcee-ai/trinity-large-preview:free","usage":{"input":22349,"output":404,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22753,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772241881413}}
