{"type":"message","id":"630319f1","parentId":"750dab5b","timestamp":"2026-02-28T01:25:53.191Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"chatcmpl-tool-807cd01d5d889bee","toolName":"web_search","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Title: Best Of 2025 Predictions & Real-Time Odds | Polymarket\nURL: https://polymarket.com/predictions/best-of-2025\nText: Best Of 2025 Predictions & Real-Time Odds | Polymarket\n\n# Best Of 2025 predictions & odds\n\n·\n\nFilter\n\n## Frequently Asked Questions\n\n### What is Polymarket?\n\nPolymarket is the world's largest prediction market, where you can stay informed and profit from your knowledge by trading on things related to breaking news, politics, sports, elections, crypto, finance, tech, culture, including topics like Best Of 2025.\n\n### What types of Best Of 2025 prediction markets can I trade on Polymarket?\n\nPolymarket currently hosts 2 active markets for Best Of 2025 that lets you track or trade on predictions like \"Most popular girl name 2025\". Whether you are tracking widely debated events or niche outcomes, the platform aggregates real-time odds based on over $1.0M in trading volume, providing a comprehensive view of fan and investor sentiment.\n\n### How do Best Of 2025 markets work on Polymarket?\n\nEach polymarket is a yes/no question. You buy shares in \"yes\" or \"no\" outcomes. Prices reflect crowd-sourced odds and probabilities. For example, if yes is at 30 cents, that's a 30% chance. Markets resolve based on official results. \n\nTitle: All Predictions & Real-Time Odds | Polymarket\nURL: https://polymarket.com/predictions/all\nText: All Predictions & Real-Time Odds | Polymarket\n\n# All predictions & odds\n\n·\n\nFilter\n\n## Frequently Asked Questions\n\n### What is Polymarket?\n\nPolymarket is the world's largest prediction market, where you can stay informed and profit from your knowledge by trading on things related to breaking news, politics, sports, elections, crypto, finance, tech, culture, including topics like All.\n\n### What types of All prediction markets can I trade on Polymarket?\n\nPolymarket currently hosts 7786 active markets for All that lets you track or trade on predictions like \"US strikes Iran by...?\". Whether you are tracking widely debated events or niche outcomes, the platform aggregates real-time odds based on over $3.5B in trading volume, providing a comprehensive view of fan and investor sentiment.\n\n### How do All markets work on Polymarket?\n\nEach polymarket is a yes/no question. You buy shares in \"yes\" or \"no\" outcomes. Prices reflect crowd-sourced odds and probabilities. For example, if yes is at 30 cents, that's a 30% chance. Markets resolve based on official results. For multi-outcome events, like \"Democratic Presidential Nominee 2028,\" you\n\nTitle: List Predictions & Real-Time Odds | Polymarket\nURL: https://polymarket.com/predictions/list\nText: List Predictions & Real-Time Odds | Polymarket\n\n# List predictions & odds\n\n·\n\n[All] \n\n[Politics] \n\n[Trump] \n\n[Culture] \n\n[Epstein] \n\n[Declassification] \n\n[Trump Presidency] \n\n[Kash Patel] \n\n[List] \n\nList· [Trump] \n\nWho will be named in newly released Epstein files by March 31?\n\nOprah Winfrey\n\n+ 45 more\n\n$959K Vol.\n\nEnds in about 1 month\n\nList· [Politics] \n\nTrump releases Epstein list today?\n\nYes\n\n$9M Vol.\n\n[1,017] \n\nList· [Politics] \n\n>100 redactions in Epstein files?\n\nYes\n\n$11.7K Vol.\n\n[19] \n\nList· [Trump] \n\nWho will be named in Epstein files by June 30?\n\nAnderson Cooper\n\n+ 35 more\n\n$4M Vol.\n\n[180] \n\nList· [Trump] \n\nWho will be named in newly released Epstein files in 2025?\n\nOprah Winfrey\n\n+ 39 more\n\n$22M Vol.\n\nFilter\n\n## Frequently Asked Questions\n\n### What is Polymarket?\n\nPolymarket is the world's largest prediction market, where you can stay informed and profit from your knowledge by trading on things related to breaking news, politics, sports, elections, crypto, finance, tech, culture, including t